Low-Light Vision		KEY:Duskling ~ Low-Light Vision	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Race Trait.Duskling Race Trait.SpecialQuality	DESC:Dusklings can see twice as far as humans in starlight, moonlight, torchlight, and similar conditions of poor illumination. They retain the ability to distinguish color and detail under these conditions.																																																																																																						SOURCEPAGE:p.10
