Thunderstep Boots					KEY:Soulborn Soulmeld ~ Thunderstep Boots					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Soulmeld.ChakraFeet.Soulborn.SoulbornChakraFeet																																																																							DESC:You shape incarnum into a pair of heavy boots that fit over your feet and any other boots you might wear. Cobalt steel forms rings around your calves and reinforces the toes of the boots. The legendary soulborn Odravan the Red was known for charging into battle wearing thunderstep boots at the head of a well-trained mercenary unit. Foes who survived Odravan's charge were usually stunned and quickly fell to his allies' swords. When you charge, your thunderstep boots channel sonic energy into your attack. If you hit with a melee attack at the end of a charge, the target takes an additional 1d4 points of sonic damage. Essentia: Every point of essentia you invest in your thunderstep boots increases the damage dealt by 1d4 points.	DESC:Chakra Bind (Feet) Your thunderstep boots bind themselves to your feet. Any creature taking damage from your thunderstep boots is also stunned for 1 round. A successful Fortitude save negates this effect.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																						SOURCEPAGE:p.90				ASPECT:Descriptors|Sonic	ASPECT:Chakra|Feet	ASPECT:Saving 