y|AUTOMATIC|Resistance to Fire																																																																																																																																																														BONUS:SLOTS|Waist|-1		BONUS:VAR|ChakraBindWaist|1	BONUS:VAR|TotemistChakraBindWaist|-1	BONUS:VAR|TotemistSoulmeldApplied|1																																SOURCEPAGE:p.82
